headline: 2 Stocks That Have More Than Doubled in the Past Year to Buy and Hold for a Decade
summary: Equity markets recently dipped due to concerns of deteriorating macroeconomic conditions, with the latest trigger being President Trump's trade wars.  Summit Therapeutics (NASDAQ: SMMT) and Robinhood Markets (NASDAQ: HOOD) belong on that list.  Here is why Summit Therapeutics and Robinhood could deliver strong returns through the next decade.
